{"tid":792460,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【鐵漢柔情你老味】成龍邀周杰倫寫歌表白林鳳嬌「謝謝一輩子」","createTime":"2018-08-24T14:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:17.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d658a3a19ae43f8be6f872db9ee5c145e08477aa","tid":792460,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:39:10.000Z","msg":"成龍一段口白感性道出，或許自己的婚姻並不完美，自己也從來不是一個好愛人，不過「每個人的生活在別人眼裡是一個樣子，但只有我們自己才真正的知道我們自己的樣子」，兩人也經歷過所有平凡夫妻的瑣碎生活，也經歷過別人無法想像的風風雨雨，一轉眼，已經過去幾十年了，「很多曾經恩愛無比的夫妻都分開了，我們兩個今天依然在一起，很多時候比一般夫妻都開心，我們越來越珍惜對方，我倆一路走到現在，一定是我付出的少，她付出的多，這輩子能遇到她，是我最大的福氣」。<br />\n<br />\n而成龍也邀請周杰倫替他量身打造一首屬於他跟林鳳嬌的歌，《謝謝一輩子》字裡行間的暖意，讓人真實感受到成龍對林鳳嬌的深情與依戀。歌詞道出自己與林鳳嬌的婚姻生活，37年的感情、36年的婚姻，成龍濃縮成3個字「謝謝」，成龍過去也曾說過，「我從來沒對嬌姐（林鳳嬌）說過我愛你，但是我經常跟她講謝謝你，這三個字，我是要講一輩子的」。36年前成龍與林鳳嬌相戀，但只能在洛杉磯一間小咖啡廳舉行簡陋的婚禮，36年後，他們依然相守相依。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v_gn62etAQ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv_gn62etAQ0&d=sF0Pb0B18CkJn4xbHXEfCb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=08fd73e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v_gn62etAQ0</a>"},{"pid":"c9a1447dc5ee754ec5186c5b25a96c9b60b77ecd","tid":792460,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成龍濃縮成3個字「謝謝」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ccc2f4f6fdcd110a5fd0cb181c8b83f3e6ec38","tid":792460,"uid":129288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"偷食就偷食啦 仲要扮撚曬好男人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e0fb6028049c3a76c56b0c5d1e2d4c8415ced6","tid":792460,"uid":85424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:38:50.000Z","msg":"無啲新意 將之前中國風嘅歌改一改就比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0782f0a8f0db25eec628065767a50d8e3e94f1e","tid":792460,"uid":43687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a1447dc5ee754ec5186c5b25a96c9b60b77ecd","tid":792460,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成龍濃縮成3個字「謝謝」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:43:35.000Z","msg":"多撚謝"},{"pid":"cde767831b5a19eab66f840a09e1da5a1cca8365","tid":792460,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"Rapist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}